        I am a <strong>Research Scientist</strong> at <a href="https://www.unimore.it">UniMORE</a> (University of Modena and Reggio Emilia),
        Department of Engineering "Enzo Ferrari", focusing on the application of <strong>Artificial Intelligence</strong>
