        Spoke 3 "Green manufacturing for a sustainable economy", developing innovative data-driven and lean-based solutions
        for sustainable production planning and control systems.
      </p>

      <p>
        Beyond research, I am a proficient <strong>Full-stack Developer</strong>, leveraging Python, JavaScript, and SQL
